Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.25,0:00:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandpa Gon's boat shot?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.96,0:00:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You did what?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.30,0:00:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,During a round?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.55,0:00:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.63,0:00:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.55,0:00:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that's what I like to hear!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.68,0:00:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the Tonbo I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.55,0:00:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I can just imagine their\Nfaces when they saw that!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.06,0:00:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not that funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.73,0:00:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tonbo hasn't changed at all. But...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.90,0:00:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Tonbo.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.57,0:00:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to see you take a shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.70,0:00:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.67,0:02:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let your guard down just yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.05,0:02:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's still only day two.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.17,0:02:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're not in first place\Nat the end it'll all be for nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.55,0:02:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Hinoki.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.68,0:02:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,She's still practicing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.93,0:02:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. You're starting now?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.43,0:02:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just grasping at straws.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.69,0:02:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Hinoki is six strokes ahead of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.02,0:02:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You're out of luck, I'm afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.32,0:02:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.36,0:02:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.82,0:02:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,See you tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.37,0:02:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tonbo. I'm sorry. I have to win. I must.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.79,0:02:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Forgive me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.04,0:02:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So you've added a six\Nand nine iron to your bag?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.13,0:02:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Who gave them to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.01,0:02:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,My dad gave her the six iron,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.13,0:03:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,and she got the nine iron\N from Mr. Nakase at the country club.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.39,0:03:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Three, six, nine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.51,0:03:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,A wedge.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.89,0:03:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd say that counts\Nas a full set for Tonbo!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.31,0:03:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,This will be a great setup for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.56,0:03:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Here I go. Starting with a swallow ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.32,0:03:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Osprey ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.91,0:03:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,A thin slice!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.16,0:03:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hajime.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.79,0:03:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't trained her at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.16,0:03:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.17,0:03:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't able to.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.25,0:03:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I worry that if she adjusts even one thing
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.71,0:03:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,she'll end up having to adjust\Nevery aspect of her game
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.80,0:03:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I fear that would
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.97,0:03:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,throw Tonbo's game off entirely.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.72,0:03:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I want her to keep playing\Nwith a free spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.35,0:03:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hajime.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.44,0:03:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad I put her in your care.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.65,0:04:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,However,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.69,0:04:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,since coming to Kumamoto, Tonbo\Nhas been hitting from the mat every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.95,0:04:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,That's starting to show in her swing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.12,0:04:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Practice mats
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.45,0:04:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,become worn down in the center,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.29,0:04:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,causing the left edge\Nto be slightly elevated.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.83,0:04:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Placing the ball there
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.34,0:04:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,creates a slight\Nuphill lie for the left foot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.80,0:04:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That creates a small space\Nbetween the ground and the ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.63,0:04:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,This is causing Tonbo's swing to relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.60,0:04:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Due to the slope of the mat, the right eye\Nis about half a ball's width lower
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.68,0:04:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,and the bridge of her nose\Ntilts to the right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.85,0:04:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Tonbo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.61,0:04:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Hit here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.86,0:04:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.24,0:04:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's aligned her eyes{\i0}\N{\i1}with the tilt of the turf. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.04,0:04:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She instinctively{\i0}\N{\i1}adjusts her setup to match the lie.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.58,0:04:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is one of Tonbo's many skills.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.63,0:05:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What changed? What did he change?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.26,0:05:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The trajectory got a bit lower.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.76,0:05:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Place the ball\Nwherever you like this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.51,0:05:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have a hat?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.06,0:05:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I have one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.64,0:05:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Hinoki gave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.64,0:05:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Make sure both ends\Nof the bill are parallel.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.90,0:05:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Just make sure\Nthe right end isn't lower.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.78,0:05:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay if the left side is lower.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.03,0:05:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.62,0:05:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright. Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.51,0:05:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The sound changed.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.88,0:05:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Igarashi has been watching her for solong.{\i0}\N{\i1}He knows just what to adjust.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.39,0:05:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Tonbo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.68,0:05:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Try hitting barefoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.19,0:05:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It tickles.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.65,0:06:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I knew it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.69,0:06:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's lifting her left big toe.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.40,0:06:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The toe she used to keep her grip{\i0}\N{\i1}on the wet floor of the fishing boat.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.32,0:06:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Tonbo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.32,0:06:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember that tool you used \Nto dispatch octopi and fish?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.12,0:06:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.25,0:06:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Imagine you're using that tool to pin\Nyour toes to the ground when you hit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.54,0:06:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That sounds painful!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.25,0:06:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just pretend!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.00,0:06:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not actually using it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.76,0:06:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean I should stay still?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.55,0:06:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.55,0:06:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,In a golf swing,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.89,0:06:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,you must move some parts of your body\Nand keep others perfectly still.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.27,0:06:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The toes of your left foot mustn't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.85,0:06:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.77,0:06:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.77,0:06:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just like this.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.40,0:06:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The sound changed again.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.36,0:06:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.37,0:06:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Even when you hit a fade,\Ndon't forget to keep track of your toes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.45,0:06:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got to focus on your feet,\Nnot just your hips.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.46,0:06:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.58,0:07:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.88,0:07:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.09,0:07:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I just thought,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.96,0:07:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,you should be the one giving her lessons.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.34,0:07:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I just made a few minor adjustments.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.47,0:07:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,If she puts too much strain\Non her body to control her swing,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.89,0:07:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,she'll be feeling it tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.60,0:07:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.73,0:07:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You should lower the net down tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.98,0:07:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The wind might start\Nblowing in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.11,0:07:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Ready to call it a night?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.15,0:07:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.36,0:07:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The weather report didn't mention that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.16,0:07:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,They mentioned rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.49,0:07:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Not the wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.74,0:07:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Igaiga.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.87,0:07:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,He's becoming more like Grandpa Gon!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.67,0:07:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay here tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.75,0:07:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I couldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.80,0:07:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That's far too generous of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.47,0:07:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of all those foolish things you did\Nwhen you were playing for us,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.22,0:07:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,my husband's reputation\Nwas dragged through the mud.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.77,0:08:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's no matter.\NWater under the bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.60,0:08:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.15,0:08:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You're taking care of Tonbo, too
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.94,0:08:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't possibly ask of anything more.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.99,0:08:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't possibly ask you\Nto take care of me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.99,0:08:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,-I couldn't.\N-You're already changing in pajamas!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.46,0:08:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,How's Grandpa Gon doing?\NIs he still sticking to only three drinks?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.79,0:08:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't speak on his drinking, but he's\Ndoing just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.51,0:08:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's almost flying fish season, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.01,0:08:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The busiest time of the year.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.01,0:08:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't be able to help him fillet the\Nfish this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.27,0:08:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Tonbo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.52,0:08:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,About tomorrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.27,0:08:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,strong winds will dry out the green.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.53,0:08:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,-That's why--\N-How's Setsu-ba?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.03,0:08:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish I could help her at the inn.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.07,0:08:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Making dinner by herself must be tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.82,0:09:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,She's persevering like she always does.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.12,0:09:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What about Mom and Dad's grave?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.54,0:09:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's lined with flowers every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.54,0:09:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I visit from time to time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.92,0:09:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.01,0:09:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Tonbo looked so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.93,0:09:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Igarashi is like\Na father to her, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.68,0:09:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? Wataru is still playing golf?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.93,0:09:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Bunpei must be getting nervous!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.69,0:09:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Bunpei is doing just fine, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.94,0:09:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Bunpei and Yoko,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.86,0:09:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,are they getting along?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.69,0:09:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if he still thinks of her
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.07,0:09:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,while he eats an ice cream after visiting\Nthe hot springs?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.08,0:09:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Igaiga?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.46,0:09:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.88,0:09:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.89,0:10:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Nikome!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.60,0:10:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Nana! Momoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.48,0:10:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,We're in the same group this week!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.48,0:10:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm looking forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.23,0:10:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I am too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.98,0:10:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.23,0:10:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,how's that girl doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.49,0:10:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,She was in first place on the first day,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.24,0:10:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,but fell off on the second.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.99,0:10:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I think she's in\Nfourth place with an even par.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.74,0:10:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,She's only got seven, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.45,0:10:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Seven?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.75,0:10:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Seven of what?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.29,0:10:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Seven clubs!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.17,0:10:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.17,0:10:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the final day.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.26,0:10:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Hinoki Otoha is at six\Nunder.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.43,0:10:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsubura Adaniya and Ema Kurisu\Nare both at five under.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.35,0:10:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,They're the only three under par.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.77,0:10:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Tonbo Oi is in fourth place,\Nfive strokes behind with an even par.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.02,0:10:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems like one of the \Ntop three will likely take the win.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.53,0:10:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Although Tonbo Oi and\Nher half set of clubs
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.07,0:11:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,taking the victory at the very end
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.95,0:11:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,would have made for a better story.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.20,0:11:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It really is windy today!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.54,0:11:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.96,0:11:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Your weather report was way off.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.92,0:11:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You really are like Grandpa Gon!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.30,0:11:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm off!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.39,0:11:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Tombo is acting different today. \NI know what it must be.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.81,0:11:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.36,0:11:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.74,0:11:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, could I get today's pin sheet?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.78,0:11:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They saved the most{\i0}\N{\i1}difficult holes for the last day.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.37,0:11:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There are a lot of pins{\i0}\N{\i1}placed near bunkers.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.92,0:11:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Emma is hitting the ball quite high.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.17,0:12:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Proof that her spin is incredible. She can{\i0}\N{\i1}make the ball stop better than anyone.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.26,0:12:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She'll have the best chance{\i0}\N{\i1}with today's pin positions.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.81,0:12:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've finally got a chance to win.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.31,0:12:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have to make it happen.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.56,0:12:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've been waiting ten years for this.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.73,0:12:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I feel confident.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.82,0:12:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm only nervous...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.82,0:12:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...about one thing.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.74,0:12:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you surprised when you heard\NI was in first place on day one?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.08,0:12:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, it didn't surprise\Nme all that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.88,0:12:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.13,0:12:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I was happy more than anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.00,0:12:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Very happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.55,0:12:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And not only me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.47,0:12:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone on the island was smiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.39,0:12:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone on the island is rooting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.64,0:12:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.14,0:12:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,you've become the pride\Nof the whole island.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.90,0:12:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You really are an island girl, Tonbo.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.24,0:13:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone was happy. I made them smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.66,0:13:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm doing this for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.16,0:13:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.25,0:13:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You must get three strokes under today.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.17,0:13:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can get your score\Nto nine under, you can't lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.67,0:13:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll make the playoffs.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.59,0:13:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it? Three strokes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.92,0:13:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My goal is sixty-nine.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.59,0:13:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll try to get two strokes{\i0}\N{\i1}under in the first half.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.89,0:13:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,How unfortunate.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.44,0:13:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't be able to play with you today.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.65,0:13:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Today we're playing in groups of three.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.27,0:13:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You're with Tsubura's\Nlast group today, right, Hata?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.65,0:13:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's the caddy for my group?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.28,0:13:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.91,0:13:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall I polish your balls?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.78,0:13:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,No thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.66,0:13:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Mr. Nishi, caddy-in-training.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.91,0:13:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,He failed the pro test four times.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.29,0:13:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't need to mention that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.17,0:14:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Tonbo Oi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.92,0:14:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.46,0:14:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.92,0:14:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.55,0:14:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I heard the rumors. She really only has{\i0}\N{\i1}seven clubs. Can she play like that?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.39,0:14:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why do I have to caddy for this kid?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.60,0:14:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} Why did Mr. Nakase tell me to do this?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.08,0:14:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with that face?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.33,0:14:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Igaiga.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.08,0:14:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You really are like Grandpa Gon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.96,0:14:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Kasahara, you'll mark for Ms. Okawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.50,0:14:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Oi, you'll mark for Ms. Kasahara.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.01,0:14:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Okawa, you'll mark for Ms. Oi, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.93,0:14:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Can I get ahead{\i0}\N{\i1}three strokes in this wind?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.35,0:14:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's another thing{\i0}\N{\i1}to be nervous about.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.52,0:15:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My strokes have a lot of spin and are weak{\i0}\N{\i1}to wind. That's the only way I can hit.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.11,0:15:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm used to playing in the wind. I don't{\i0}\N{\i1}mind it. But I'm not the only one.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.86,0:15:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's someone else{\i0}\N{\i1}I need to watch out for.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.87,0:15:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The forest has turned completely white.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.91,0:15:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,White?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.37,0:15:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The color of the leaves\Nwhen they're blown by the wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.38,0:15:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,When reading the wind,\Ngolfers must pay attention to the trees.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.01,0:15:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Pros look at the color of the leaves.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.88,0:15:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,When it's blowing this hard,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.76,0:15:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,even Bunpei can tell\Nwhere it's coming from.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.39,0:15:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,That's because he's\Nreally good at reading the wind!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.14,0:15:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's Bunpei?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.02,0:15:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The king of{\i1} goro {\i0}golf.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.73,0:15:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Goro {\i0}golf?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.57,0:15:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I'll try{\i1} goro {\i0}golf today, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.03,0:15:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's how they do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.66,0:15:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That's so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.30,0:16:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The wind carried it all the\Nway into the left forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.60,0:16:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got to tie it a bit tighter.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.77,0:16:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! You're next!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.81,0:16:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The hole starts with a grove on the right.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.61,0:16:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll probably have to aim{\i0}\N{\i1}for the adjacent hole,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.61,0:16:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but aiming that far right{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.11,0:16:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}is scary.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.08,0:16:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even with a flat fairway, landing the ball{\i0}\N{\i1}in the right place will be tough.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.84,0:16:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The band will break\Nif you pull too hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.71,0:16:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll need a hairpin, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.68,0:16:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.97,0:16:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not alright! You have to hit!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.14,0:17:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I'm going to use this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.10,0:17:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,A five wood?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.98,0:17:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Tonbo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.02,0:17:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about your score!\NGet out there and win this thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.99,0:17:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Play your way!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.40,0:17:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Show us that special Tonbo style!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.24,0:17:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.54,0:17:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Teeing up high in wind like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.04,0:17:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is she aiming?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.92,0:17:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Tonbo's going for a swallow ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.42,0:17:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But why is she using a five wood?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.84,0:17:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Her driver is designed\Nto produce as little spin as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.18,0:17:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Not only backspin, but\Ncreating side spin is difficult as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.93,0:17:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hard to turn the ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.02,0:17:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Because a five wood is usually\Nhit from the ground,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.94,0:17:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,it's designed to create backspin\Nto send the ball up high.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.19,0:17:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's easy to turn the ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.57,0:17:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,She's not aiming for a swallow ball.\NShe's looking to improve her score.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.58,0:18:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What? The wind isn't carrying it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.46,0:18:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Go! Flying fish ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.88,0:18:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.80,0:18:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The ball has a fierce cut spin sending it\Nstraight through the wind, unharmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.68,0:18:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no! My visor is gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.56,0:18:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.68,0:18:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The visor Hinoki gave me! Where'd it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.93,0:18:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Her concentration is incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.90,0:18:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even in this wind, she's able to{\i0}\N{\i1}send the ball any direction she wants{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.65,0:18:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's like a fish in water.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.44,0:18:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! We have to get going!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.07,0:18:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll find it for you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.70,0:18:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.12,0:18:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,She's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.37,0:18:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How is she able to turn the ball?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.46,0:18:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Her swing is different{\i0}\N{\i1}every shot she takes!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.93,0:19:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This one won't be easy. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.06,0:19:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sandy lies with thin grass.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.65,0:19:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's even a bunker{\i0}\N{\i1}between the ball and the pin.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.52,0:19:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.03,0:19:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That stance!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.82,0:19:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,She avoided the sand!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.00,0:19:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.12,0:19:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew that would work! This is so fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.12,0:19:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You knew it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.38,0:19:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean you had confidence in that shot?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.13,0:19:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you scared of anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.80,0:19:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.76,0:19:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a terrifying shot!\NWhat if you went in the bunker?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.01,0:19:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.01,0:19:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I just thought it'd be cool if I could get\Nit over the bunker!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.89,0:19:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Cool?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.52,0:19:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I avoided hitting a chunk shot\Nwith my stance!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.64,0:19:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What? But how?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.02,0:19:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.37,0:20:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's where Tonbo hit.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.88,0:20:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even in this strong wind,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.67,0:21:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} she's aiming her swings{\i0}\N{\i1}towards the seventh hole on the left.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.09,0:21:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm sure she hit that cut ball{\i0}\N{\i1}to battle the wind,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.72,0:21:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but I don't plan on fighting the wind.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.81,0:21:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} I'm going to use it to my advantage.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.35,0:21:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's how I deal with wind.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.56,0:21:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I just have to get the ball{\i0}\N{\i1}on the wide left area of the pin.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.91,0:21:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It won't make it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.96,0:21:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.79,0:21:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey Tsubura! How's it going?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.79,0:21:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What does it look like? My ball is way\Nover here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.30,0:21:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,How about you, Tonbo?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.34,0:21:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,My score hasn't changed yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.93,0:21:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Adaniya got a double bogey.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.65,0:22:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm down three strokes.{\i0}\N{\i1}Tsubura and Ema are down two.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.61,0:22:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We're all tied at three under.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.07,0:22:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I thought only the three of us had a{\i0}\N{\i1}chance to win. But Tonbo is on par.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.66,0:22:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's entered the running{\i0}\N{\i1}to win this thing!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.17,0:23:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The final day of the\Ncompetition has begun!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.55,0:23:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What's wrong, Tonbo?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.26,0:23:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.81,0:23:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,On the next episode of Tonbo!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.60,0:23:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hinoki's Troubles{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.14,0:24:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yaya asked me to choose between\Nwestern or Chinese food for dinner!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.94,0:24:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't changed at all.
